Colonels Vadym Sukharveskyi and Andrii Lebedenko will be the Commander-in-Chief's deputies in charge of UAVs and tech innovation, respectively.

Brigade Generals Volodymyr Horbatiuk, Oleksiy Shevchenko, and Mykhailo Drapatyi will serve as the Head of General Staff's deputies in charge of operational planning and management, logistics, and training.

Commander-in-Chief, commanders, and officials were all present. Clear tasks on financing and speeding up contracts. Everything planned for this year will be implemented.
